  @skip
  Scenario: [5] Variable length pattern with label predicate on both sides
    Given an empty graph
    And having executed:
      """
      CREATE (a:Blue), (b:Red), (c:Green), (d:Yellow)
      CREATE (a)-[:T]->(b),
             (b)-[:T]->(c),
             (b)-[:T]->(d)
      """
    When executing query:
      """
      MATCH (a:Blue)-[r*]->(b:Green)
      RETURN count(r)
      """
